                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The paper reprints an article stating that a prominent Republican stated
                    that no white Virginian could be a "good Republican." The article jokes that if
                    he meant a "Sumner-Butler-Drake-Porter" Republican, then Virginia is better off.</summary>
                <note/>
