                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>The Deaf, Dumb, and Blind Institution Fire Company and the Augusta Fire
                    Company of Staunton turned out to parade on Saturday. Prof. Turner led the blind
                    band in a grand band wagon. Both companies appeared in full uniform with their
                    engines and reels. The paper especially thanks the band and Capt. Moon and Capt.
                    Scherer.</summary>
                <note/>
